                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/1.jpg" class="rounded-circle" alt="Member 1" style="width: 80px; height: 80px;">
                <p class="mt-3"><em>"Joining this membership has been a game-changer for me! I love the points!"</em></p>
                <strong>- Alex Johnson</strong>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="text-center">
                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/1.jpg" class="rounded-circle" alt="Member 2" style="width: 80px; height: 80px;">
                <p class="mt-3"><em>"Fantastic service and great rewards. I can't recommend it enough!"</em></p>
                <strong>- Emma Roberts</strong>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="text-center">
                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/2.jpg" class="rounded-circle" alt="Member 3" style="width: 80px; height: 80px;">
                <p class="mt-3"><em>"I earned points quickly, and they made my car wash so much cheaper!"</em></p>
